content.description: The main climbing wall area is sunny and usually sheltered from the wind. Most climbs are about 50-70 ft here. This place has great fishing as well so bring a pole, some locals told me about this place when I was at the climbing gym in Kingston. Has some sport routes but mostly trad climbing I will try and get pictures and routes next time I am there, it may be too cold to climb on my next visit. There are other walls and areas to climb here and will explore more.
